  "texts": [
    "Academic coverage varies widely here-1 paper for automotive, 2 for property, and 3 for health insurance.",
    "Through our analysis, we identified three critical research gaps.",
    "First, property insurance lacks academic attention in both policyholder behavior analysis and claims automation.",
    "Industry has implemented these solutions, but research lags behind.",
    "Second, strategic decision-making shows consistent industry adoption with 3 implementations per domain."
  ]
